  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Comparison of the serum adiponectin level at the end of study (6 weeks) between the two groups.</measure>
  </primary_outcome>
  <secondary_outcome>
    <measure>Comparison of serum level of TNF alpha, IL-6, leptine, hsCRP, TG, HDL and blood pressure control between two groups. Adipocyte differentiation in 30 patients (PPAR gamma stimulation) between two groups.</measure>
  </secondary_outcome>
